   1 # -*- coding=utf-8 -*-
   2 from __future__ import absolute_import, print_function

   4 import importlib
   5 import os
   6 import sys
   7 
   8 from pipenv.vendor import attr
   9 import pip_shims
  10 import six
  11 
  12 from ..environment import MYPY_RUNNING
  13 from .url import URI

  15 if MYPY_RUNNING:
  16     from typing import Any, Optional, Tuple

  19 @attr.s(hash=True)
  20 class VCSRepository(object):
  21     DEFAULT_RUN_ARGS = None
  22 
  23     url = attr.ib()  # type: str
  24     name = attr.ib()  # type: str
  25     checkout_directory = attr.ib()  # type: str
  26     vcs_type = attr.ib()  # type: str
  27     parsed_url = attr.ib()  # type: URI
  28     subdirectory = attr.ib(default=None)  # type: Optional[str]
  29     commit_sha = attr.ib(default=None)  # type: Optional[str]
  30     ref = attr.ib(default=None)  # type: Optional[str]
  31     repo_backend = attr.ib()  # type: Any
  32     clone_log = attr.ib(default=None)  # type: Optional[str]
  33 
  34     @parsed_url.default
  35     def get_parsed_url(self):
  36         # type: () -> URI
  37         return URI.parse(self.url)
  38 
  39     @repo_backend.default
  40     def get_repo_backend(self):
  41         if self.DEFAULT_RUN_ARGS is None:
  42             default_run_args = self.monkeypatch_pip()
  43         else:
  44             default_run_args = self.DEFAULT_RUN_ARGS
  45         from pip_shims.shims import VcsSupport
  46 
  47         VCS_SUPPORT = VcsSupport()
  48         backend = VCS_SUPPORT.get_backend(self.vcs_type)
  49         # repo = backend(url=self.url)
  50         if backend.run_command.__func__.__defaults__ != default_run_args:
  51             backend.run_command.__func__.__defaults__ = default_run_args
  52         return backend
  53 
  54     @property
  55     def is_local(self):
  56         # type: () -> bool
  57         url = self.url
  58         if "+" in url:
  59             url = url.split("+")[1]
  60         return url.startswith("file")
  61 
  62     def obtain(self):
  63         # type: () -> None
  64         lt_pip_19_2 = (
  65             pip_shims.parsed_pip_version.parsed_version < pip_shims.parse_version("19.2")
  66         )
  67         if lt_pip_19_2:
  68             self.repo_backend = self.repo_backend(self.url)
  69         if os.path.exists(
  70             self.checkout_directory
  71         ) and not self.repo_backend.is_repository_directory(self.checkout_directory):
  72             self.repo_backend.unpack(self.checkout_directory)
  73         elif not os.path.exists(self.checkout_directory):
  74             if lt_pip_19_2:
  75                 self.repo_backend.obtain(self.checkout_directory)
  76             else:
  77                 self.repo_backend.obtain(self.checkout_directory, self.parsed_url)
  78         else:
  79             if self.ref:
  80                 self.checkout_ref(self.ref)
  81         if not self.commit_sha:
  82             self.commit_sha = self.get_commit_hash()
  83 
  84     def checkout_ref(self, ref):
  85         # type: (str) -> None
  86         rev_opts = self.repo_backend.make_rev_options(ref)
  87         if not any(
  88             [
  89                 self.repo_backend.is_commit_id_equal(self.checkout_directory, ref),
  90                 self.repo_backend.is_commit_id_equal(self.checkout_directory, rev_opts),
  91                 self.is_local,
  92             ]
  93         ):
  94             self.update(ref)
  95 
  96     def update(self, ref):
  97         # type: (str) -> None
  98         target_ref = self.repo_backend.make_rev_options(ref)
  99         if pip_shims.parse_version(pip_shims.pip_version) > pip_shims.parse_version(
 100             "18.0"
 101         ):
 102             self.repo_backend.update(self.checkout_directory, self.url, target_ref)
 103         else:
 104             self.repo_backend.update(self.checkout_directory, target_ref)
 105         self.commit_sha = self.get_commit_hash()
 106 
 107     def get_commit_hash(self, ref=None):
 108         # type: (Optional[str]) -> str
 109         with pip_shims.shims.global_tempdir_manager():
 110             return self.repo_backend.get_revision(self.checkout_directory)
 111 
 112     @classmethod
 113     def monkeypatch_pip(cls):
 114         # type: () -> Tuple[Any, ...]
 115         target_module = pip_shims.shims.VcsSupport.__module__
 116         pip_vcs = importlib.import_module(target_module)
 117         run_command_defaults = pip_vcs.VersionControl.run_command.__defaults__
 118         # set the default to not write stdout, the first option sets this value
 119         new_defaults = [False] + list(run_command_defaults)[1:]
 120         new_defaults = tuple(new_defaults)
 121         if six.PY3:
 122             try:
 123                 pip_vcs.VersionControl.run_command.__defaults__ = new_defaults
 124             except AttributeError:
 125                 pip_vcs.VersionControl.run_command.__func__.__defaults__ = new_defaults
 126         else:
 127             pip_vcs.VersionControl.run_command.__func__.__defaults__ = new_defaults
 128         sys.modules[target_module] = pip_vcs
 129         cls.DEFAULT_RUN_ARGS = new_defaults
 130         return new_defaults
